title: Sergei Lushchik — Full-Stack Developer
description: Developer portfolio and blog.
---
<section id="about" class="intro section">
	<p>I became interested in software development in my early teens, starting out as a self-taught programmer before later pursuing formal coursework. By 16, I had already stepped into my first professional role in IT, working full-time during summers and part-time alongside my studies.</p>
	<p>Today, I work as a full-stack developer, building and maintaining both frontend and backend systems. I'm driven by the challenge of solving complex problems and enjoy continuously adapting to an ever-evolving technology landscape.</p>
	<p>Outside of work, I'm into photography and stay engaged in political initiatives. Occasionally, I bring those interests together.</p>
	<p>Feel free to reach out if you'd like to talk tech or connect more broadly.</p>
</section>

<section id="experience" class="section">
	<h2>Experience</h2>
	<div class="experience-list">
		{% for item in collections.experience %}
			<article class="experience-item">
				<h3>{{ item.data.title }}</h3>
				<p class="meta-row">{{ item.data.company }}
					{% if item.data.timeframe %} · {{ item.data.timeframe | displayTimeframe }}
					{% endif %}
				</p>
				<p>{{ item.content  | safe }}</p>
				{% if item.data.technologies and item.data.technologies.length %}
					<ul class="tag-list tech-tags" aria-label="Technologies">
						{% for tech in item.data.technologies %}
							<li>{{ tech }}</li>
						{% endfor %}
					</ul>
				{% endif %}
			</article>
		{% endfor %}
	</div>
</section>

